Instant kill? That's pushing the rules, alot. Probably breaking them.

::Reptilica/Bloodystrike::

Reptilica nods, taking the stuff Wheeljack handed him. He wasn't sure if he 
could make the weapon as powerful as it was invented, but he could at least 
replicate it. 

Motioning Bloodystrike to follow him, Reptilica walks toward a door, opening 
it and entering the next room, Bloodystrike following.
